Time":"2019-03-09T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"咁多人回鄉創業，中国經濟真係大好一偏，中国又赢！"},{"pid":"cf4534401f7b8ab1f57408620caf864fb699fc6e","tid":1044490,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19910090c62530c3466a86d1c8ab2d150d34ca60","tid":1044490,"uid":92811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:26:32.000Z","msg":"唔係好事<br />\n<br />\n維尼繼續泵水落去填啲無底坑先係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"印左3萬幾億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}